@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081

### Onboard new employee - Randy Broussard
# This triggers the full 8-step onboarding workflow with LLM-as-a-Judge validation.
# Steps: 1) DB inserts, 2) Image upload to GCS, 3) Badge generation, 4-7) Draft emails, 8) GCS cleanup
# The employee image (randy_broussard.jpg) and CSV data file are uploaded as multipart form data.
POST {{baseUrl}}/onboarding
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=OnboardingBoundary

--OnboardingBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="firstName"

Randy
--OnboardingBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="lastName"

Broussard
--OnboardingBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="personalEmail"

randy.broussard.personal@gmail.com
--OnboardingBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="employeeImage"; filename="randy_broussard.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ../../main/resources/images/randy_broussard.jpg
--OnboardingBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="csvFile"; filename="onboarding_randy_broussard.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ../resources/data/onboarding_randy_broussard.csv
--OnboardingBoundary--

### Verify employee was created (search by name after onboarding)
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees/search?firstName=Randy&lastName=Broussard

### Verify address was created (search by city)
GET {{baseUrl}}/addresses?city=Springfield&state=IL

### Check GCS for employee image
GET {{baseUrl}}/list-files?prefix=employees/

### Check GCS onboarding folder is cleaned up
GET {{baseUrl}}/list-files?prefix=onboarding/

### Check generated images folder
GET {{baseUrl}}/list-files?prefix=generated_images/

### Check draft emails were created
GET {{baseUrl}}/read-folder?folder=%5BGmail%5D/Drafts&subjectFilter=MegaCorp%20Onboarding&maxEmails=10

### Legacy: Generate welcome message (uses SelfRefineEvaluationAdvisor pattern)
GET {{baseUrl}}/ai/onboarding/welcome?employeeName=Randy%20Broussard&position=Software%20Engineer&startDate=2026-04-01
